name: Aglaonema
description: Delight in the elegance of Aglaonema, boasting variegated cream and green leaves. with its air-purifying qualities, it is the prfect addition to your home office.

name: Anthurium
description: Bring a touch of the tropics to your home with Anthurium. This plant features glossy, heart-shaped leaves and striking blush flowers.

name: Monstera Deliciosa
description: With its glossy green and fenestrated leaves, and aerial root system, Monstera will make a statement in your favourite room.

name: Begonia Maculata
description: With its vibrant colours and textured leaves, this beauty is sure to be a conversations starter.

name: Fiddle Leaf Fig
description: With its large, violin-shaped leaves, Fiddle Leaf Fig is a statement piece for any room.

name: Olea Europaea
description: With its silvery-green leaves and gnarled trunk, Olive Tree is a symbol of peace and abundance. It will add a touch of the Mediterranean to your home.

name: Philodendron
description: With its glossy, heart shaped leaves, Philodendron is a gorgeous climbing plant for draping along the mantlepiece.
